query:
SELECT su.id, su.userId, su.supplierId, u.email, s.companyName 
FROM supplierUsers su 
JOIN users u ON su.userId = u.id 
JOIN suppliers s ON su.supplierId = s.id 
WHERE u.email = '12@supplier.com'
